    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    brand_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id)
);

    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    gender ENUM('Male', 'Female'),
    age INT,

    product_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);


CREATE TABLE Category (
    category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);


CREATE TABLE Customer (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100)
);

    product_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);

    product_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);


CREATE TABLE Brand (
    brand_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);


CREATE TABLE Customer (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100)
);

    product_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);

    customer_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);


CREATE TABLE Category (
    category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(255),
    category_description TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE Product (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);
</t><stat>insert into brand (brand_id, brand_name) select 1, 'brand1'</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE Brand (
    brand_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);


CREATE TABLE Order (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);

    customer_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);


CREATE TABLE Category (
    category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(255),
    category_description TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE Brand (
    brand_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);


CREATE TABLE Product (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);
</t><stat>INSERT INTO Brand (brand_id, brand_name) SELECT 1, 'Brand1'</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE Order (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);

    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);


CREATE TABLE Product (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);


CREATE TABLE Order (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);
</t><stat>INSERT INTO Brand (brand_id, brand_name) SELECT 2, 'Brand2'</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE Category (
    category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(255),
    category_description TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE Customer (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);

    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);


CREATE TABLE Order (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);

    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);


CREATE TABLE Category (
    category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(255),
    category_description TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE Product (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);

    customer_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);


CREATE TABLE Category (
    category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(255),
    category_description TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE Brand (
    brand_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);


CREATE TABLE Product (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);
</t><stat>INSERT INTO Brand (brand_id, brand_name) SELECT 2, 'Brand2'</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE Order (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);

    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);


CREATE TABLE Product (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);


CREATE TABLE Order (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);
</t><stat>INSERT INTO Brand (brand_id, brand_name) SELECT 3, 'Brand3'</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE Category (
    category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(255),
    category_description TEXT
);

    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);

    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);


CREATE TABLE Order (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);

    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);


CREATE TABLE Category (
    category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(255),
    category_description TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE Product (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);

    customer_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);


CREATE TABLE Category (
    category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(255),
    category_description TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE Brand (
    brand_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);


CREATE TABLE Product (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);
</t><stat>INSERT INTO Brand (brand_id, brand_name) SELECT 3, 'Brand3'</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE Order (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);

    customer_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);


CREATE TABLE Order (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);


CREATE TABLE Category (
    category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(255),
    category_description TEXT
);
</t><stat>INSERT INTO Category (category_id, category_name, category_description) SELECT 1, 'Category1', 'Category 1 Description'</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE Brand (
    brand_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);


CREATE TABLE Product (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);

    customer_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);


CREATE TABLE Category (
    category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(255),
    category_description TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE Product (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);
</t><stat>INSERT INTO Category (category_id, category_name, category_description) SELECT 1, 'Category1', 'Category 1 Description'</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE Brand (
    brand_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);


CREATE TABLE Order (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);

    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);


CREATE TABLE Product (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);


CREATE TABLE Brand (
    brand_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);

</t><stat>INSERT INTO Category (category_id, category_name, category_description) SELECT 3, 'Category3', 'Category 3 Description'</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE Category (
    category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(255),
    category_description TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE Customer (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);


CREATE TABLE Order (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);


CREATE TABLE Product (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);

    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);

    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);

    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);


CREATE TABLE Brand (
    brand_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);

    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);


CREATE TABLE Category (
    category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(255),
    category_description TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE Brand (
    brand_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);

    category_name VARCHAR(255),
    category_description TEXT
);


CREATE TABLE Customer (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);
</t><stat>insert into product (product_id, product_name, brand_id, category_id) select 2, 'product2', 2, 2</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE Brand (
    brand_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand_name VARCHAR(255)
);


CREATE TABLE Order (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);


CREATE TABLE Product (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);

    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    brand_id INT,
    category_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (brand_id) REFERENCES Brand(brand_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES Category(category_id)
);
</t><stat>insert into product (product_id, product_name, brand_id, category_id) select 3, 'product3', 3, 3</stat><divider><t>CREATE TABLE Order (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);

    customer_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);

    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
